lead_paragraph: Former England captain Chris Robshaw is confident any residual gloom left over from last year's dismal World Cup exit will be gone by the time the team walk out to play Ireland at Twickenham in the Six Nations on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Robshaw Relishing England's Return to Twickenham
